Bad sales person

We are a very potential buyer, went there for house viewing, no one approached, 3 salesperson kept chit chatting inside the room, laughing loudly regardless customers outside viewing the house without assistance. We were there about half an hour and even gave a hint for them to approach us but they just ignored. Beautiful & spacious house, im sorry we immmediately remove Aurora Sentral from our list
Great upcoming township in Iskandar Puteri.
